{"lemma":"إِفْكَيْ","slug":"إِفْكَيْ","root":"#.ف.ك","root_slug":"_-ف-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ف-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"إِفْك","root":"أفك","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n954","n34380"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D9%81%D9%92%D9%83%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lie","examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ جَآءُو بِٱلْإِفْكِ عُصْبَةٌ مِّنْكُمْ لَا تَحْسَبُوهُ شَرًّا لَّكُم بَلْ هُوَ خَيْرٌ لَّكُمْ لِكُلِّ ٱمْرِئٍ مِّنْهُم مَّا ٱكْتَسَبَ مِنَ ٱلْإِثْمِ وَٱلَّذِي تَوَلَّى كِبْرَهُ مِنْهُمْ لَهُ عَذَابٌ عَظِيمٌ","english":"Lo! they who spread the slander are a gang among you. Deem it not a bad thing for you; nay, it is good for you. Unto every man of them (will be paid) that which he hath earned of the sin; and as for him among them who had the greater share therein, his will be an awful doom."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n954","headword_ar":"اـِفْكٌ","root":"Afk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[an inf. n. used as a subst.;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lie; a falsehood;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afiykapN","text_ar":"اَفِيكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl. (of the latter, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaAy^iku","text_ar":"اَفَايِكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA laloA^afiykapi","text_ar":"يَا لَلْاَفِيكَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA liloA^afiykapi","text_ar":"يَا لِلْاَفِيكَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laloA^afay~ikapi","text_ar":"لَلْاَفَيِّكَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", using the dim. form for the purpose of enhancement; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O the lie!"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O the great lie!"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":"with fet-h denoting calling to aid; and with kesr denoting wonder, as though the meaning were, O man, wonder thou at this great lie. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n34380","headword_ar":"اَفَكُّ","root":"fk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afak~u Almanokibi","text_ar":"اَفَكُّ المَنْكِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manokib","text_ar":"مَنْكِب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shoulder-bone"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has become unknit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loosened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ainofaraja","text_ar":"اِنْفَرَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from its joint, in consequence of weakness and flaccidity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K. * [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maforuwkN","text_ar":"مَفْرُوكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN A^afak~u","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ اَفَكُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man having the jaw broken"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [There expl. as signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masokuwru Alfak~i","text_ar":"مَسْكُورُ الفَكِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; a mistranscription, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makosuwruAlfak~i","text_ar":"مَكْسُورُالفَكِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fakakN","text_ar":"فَكَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence.])       -A2-  See also"},{"kin